column2: SELECT top # m.id AS ID, m.RA AS ra1, m.DEC AS dec1, stack.ra AS ra, stack.dec AS dec, stack.psfMag_u AS umag, stack.psfMagErr_u AS umagerr, stack.psfMag_g AS gmag, stack.psfMagErr_g AS gmagerr, stack.psfMag_r AS rmag, stack.psfMagErr_r AS rmagerr, stack.psfMag_i AS imag, stack.psfMagErr_i AS imagerr, stack.psfMag_z AS zmag, stack.psfMagErr_g AS zmagerr, stack.extinction_u AS extinction_u FROM MyDB.browncat_bootes AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS stack ON n.objid = stack.objID
